<p><strong>Brisbane, {{ date | readableDate }}</strong>
<p>OneQode has signed a Memorandum of Understanding with YAJI Software, creators of the Cocos Engine.
</p>
<div class="callout col-xs-12 p-2 my-2" id="key-facts">
	<h2>Key facts</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>OneQode has signed a Memorandum of Understanding with China-based YAJI Software, the team behind the Cocos Engine and Cocos2d-x.</li>
		<li>Cocos2d-x is one of the world’s most popular open source engines.</li>
		<li>The OneQode cloud platform will be available through the Cocos Marketplace, allowing OneQode to provide a frictionless experience for developers using the Cocos Engine.</li>
	</ul>
</div>
<p>The agreement will place OneQode’s cloud offering in the Cocos Marketplace, giving developers using the engine direct access to OneQode’s high-performance compute and latency-optimized network.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.cocos.com/" target="_blank">Cocos</a> will be able to expand its service by partnering with OneQode, providing OneQode’s cloud and network capability to its 1.4 million registered developers and 1.6 billion gamers.</p>
